# Unity strict allowlist: keep only user-authored project content.
# Everything is ignored by default, then we explicitly include what we want to track.
*

# Keep this file
!.gitignore

# Keep all user-created/modified assets (scenes, prefabs, scripts, materials, textures, etc.)
!Assets/
!Assets/**

# Remove Vuforia Engine-related assets from tracking
Assets/**/Vuforia/
Assets/**/Vuforia/**
QCAR/
QCAR/**
Assets/Editor/Migration/com.ptc.vuforia.engine-11.4.4.tgz
Assets/Editor/Migration/com.ptc.vuforia.engine-11.4.4.tgz.meta

# Keep package definitions required to restore dependencies
!Packages/
!Packages/manifest.json
!Packages/packages-lock.json

# Keep full project settings for reproducible project behavior on other machines
!ProjectSettings/
!ProjectSettings/**
